Plain text
SECRET
  ↓
Encrypt with AES-256-GCM
  ↓
Split recovery key into 5 shards
  ↓
Protect each shard with passphrase-derived keys
  ↓
Store locally as JSON files
  ↓
Recover using any 3 shards
  ↓
Write signed local recovery log
Everything runs:
locally
offline
without cloud services
without blockchain
without biometrics
